>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a923fb7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"a923fb7\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7863e6d elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"7863e6d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4eaab2a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4eaab2a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tons Of New Fixes & Enhancements For Better Accessibility</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-38b8942 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"38b8942\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed9c873 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"ed9c873\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed1c8e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ed1c8e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WordPress constantly improves accessibility with every new release, and WordPress 5.5 is no exception. With this upcoming release, WordPress users will get tons of new fixes and enhancements for better accessibility such as:</span></p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">List tables with extensive and alternate view modes</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ability to convert link-list widgets to HTML5 navigation blocks</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ability to copy links in media screens and modal dialogues with a single click</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Meta boxes that move with keyboard</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Custom logos on front page will no longer link to front page</span></li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Better appearance for disabled buttons so that they actually look disabled</span></li></ul></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a13471 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"5a13471\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5cb105d elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"5cb105d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d7047a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6d7047a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">New Changes For WordPress Developers</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75d9bff elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"75d9bff\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f640a7d elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"f640a7d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a76c731 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a76c731\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With <strong>WordPress 5.5</strong>, developers will also be able to explore and test many new changes which they can utilize in developing their own plugins, themes and more. They can even </span><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/15/controlling-plugin-and-theme-auto-updates-ui-in-wordpress-5-5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>control the auto-updates</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> for their own plugins and themes if they want to.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Besides this, WordPress 5.5 will also come with </span><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/01/external-library-updates-in-wordpress-5-5-call-for-testing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>several updated external libraries</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> such as phpMailer, SimplePie, Twemoji and much more.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac3a79a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"ac3a79a\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efa8fbc elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"efa8fbc\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b4185b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0b4185b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Ready To Get Started With WordPress 5.5?</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-251ad22 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"251ad22\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aebf2d0 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"aebf2d0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33fd8d2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33fd8d2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although WordPress 5.5 is still in beta, you can check out the features mentioned in this post and test them for yourself on a local site by using </span><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-beta-tester/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>WordPress Beta Tester</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> plugin. Alternatively, you can also install the zip file for WordPress 5.5 and install it on your local site to test these new upcoming features.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are new to WordPress and would like to know more about how to use it, we have several blog posts that might interest you. Check out our tutorial on how to move your blog </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wordpress-com-to-wordpress-org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>from WordPress.com to WordPress.org</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, our step-by-step guide on how to </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/clear-wordpress-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>clear WordPress cache</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> or, if you want to start a fresh new website, find out how to </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/how-to-delete-wordpress-account/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>delete WordPress Account</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b73f251 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"b73f251\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4603978 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"4603978\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62f84b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"62f84b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n			<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Final Thoughts</h2>		</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n				<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-787b4ab elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"787b4ab\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n						<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56b9909 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"56b9909\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n			<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a5fe1bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a5fe1bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n				<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n					<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Are you excited for <strong>WordPress 5.5</strong>? Share your thoughts with us and let us know which of these new features you are most interested in. For more news, tutorials and updates, be sure to </span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/blog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>subscribe to our blog</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> or join our </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/wpdeveloper.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><b>Facebook community</b></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> to connect with other WordPress users like yourself.</span></p></div>\n				</div>\n				</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n						</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n		<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wordpress-5-5-new-features/\">WordPress 5.5 New Features: What&#8217;s Coming In Next Release</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net\">WPDeveloper</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wordpress-5-5-new-features/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"c