(164, 1, '2020-08-02 17:31:40', '2020-08-02 17:31:40', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">PRODUCT</h1>		\n											<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/catalog/us/companies/773/boconcept\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n							<img width=\"257\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-257x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-257x300.png 257w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture.png 453w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 257px) 100vw, 257px\" />								</a>\n											<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/catalog/us/companies/773/boconcept\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n							<img width=\"330\" height=\"70\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_1000px-BoConcept-Logo.svg.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_1000px-BoConcept-Logo.svg.png 330w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_1000px-BoConcept-Logo.svg-300x64.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\" />								</a>\n		<p>BoConcept was born in Denmark in 1952, and is today a premium retail lifestyle brand. They design, produce and sell a range of contemporary Danish design furniture, accessories and lighting for the living room, dining room, bedroom, home-office and outdoor spaces. Their furniture stores offer everything within modern design ranging from designer sofas and armchairs to practical wall units and functional TV units. BoConcept also helps their customers create a personal home with their comprehensive in home or store Interior Design service.</p>		\n											<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/catalog/us/companies/900/egger\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n							<img width=\"242\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-1-242x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-1-242x300.png 242w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-1.png 472w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 242px) 100vw, 242px\" />								</a>\n											<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/catalog/us/companies/900/egger\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n							<img width=\"330\" height=\"87\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_Screenshot_2016-10-13_16.08.52.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_Screenshot_2016-10-13_16.08.52.png 330w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_Screenshot_2016-10-13_16.08.52-300x79.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\" />								</a>\n		<p>EGGER is a steadily growing, global family company founded in 1961 with headquarters in St. Johann, Tyrol, Austria. Under the motto \"More from wood\", EGGER\'s 9,000 employees, in 18 locations worldwide, produce a comprehensive range of products made of wood-based materials (chipboard, OSB and MDF boards), as well as timber. EGGER products are found in countless areas of private and public life: in kitchens, bathrooms, offices, hotels and shops. EGGER is a full-range supplier for the furniture industry and interior design, wood construction and laminate flooring sectors. With innovative products and a growing turnover in a challenging market, EGGER is recognized as a leader in its industry.</p>		\n											<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/catalog/us/companies/261/grespania\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n							<img width=\"233\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-2-233x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-2-233x300.png 233w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Capture-2.png 479w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 233px) 100vw, 233px\" />								</a>\n											<a href=\"https://www.archdaily.com/catalog/us/companies/261/grespania\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n							<img width=\"330\" height=\"73\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_GRESPANIA_CERAMICA.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_GRESPANIA_CERAMICA.jpg 330w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/large_GRESPANIA_CERAMICA-300x66.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px\" />								</a>\n		<p>Grespania is an international company operating in 6 countries, dedicated to the manufacture and marketing of innovative ceramic products. A continued investment, incorporation of the latest developments in manufacturing and the utmost respect for the environment has consolidated its global leadership over the past 40 years. Today, Grespania is able to offer a wide range of products that help solve customer problems and improve their welfare. Grespania\'s product range has no bounds: from ideas to those looking for their homes a touch of personality and style, to technical solutions for professionals in the most demanding buildings.</p>', 'Product', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'product', '', '', '2020-08-05 19:40:01', '2020-08-05 19:40:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=164', 0, 'page', '', 0),
